                        </title>
                    </head>
                    <figure n="Gilchrist.11.1.bqscan" rend="file" width="250" height="361"/>
                    <p>Ruthven Todd is now gathering material for a final working over of his
                        edition of Gilchrist’s biography of Blake. He asks our readers to
                        send him notes containing material that they think should be added to the
                        biography. Contributors will be credited in print for their assistance.
                        Todd’s address is Ca’n Bieló, Galilea,
                        Mallorca, Spain.</p>
                </div2>
